name: PregnancyNewICD10CodesPublishedBetween2018And2020
title: Pregnancy (New ICD10 codes published between 2018 and 2020)
description: This value set is currently undergoing testing. Until it is validated, please use caution if using this value set.
purpose: (Clinical Focus: Pregnancy),(Data Element Scope: New ICD10 codes released between 2018 and 2020 to represent pregnancy. This value set was created to expand the PCPI pregnancy value set (2.16.840.1.113883.3.526.3.378). Note: there were no new ICD10-CM codes published in 2020 that represent pregnancy.),(Inclusion Criteria: ICD10 codes released between 2018 and 2020 that represent pregnancy.),(Exclusion Criteria: ICD10 codes released before 2018 and after 2020 that represent pregnancy, along with all other standard terminology codes that represent pregnancy (e.g., SNOMED-CT))
